Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.11,0:22:25.91,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}Does it get easier with time for the immortal?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.53,0:22:28.91,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}If I was born normal
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.08,0:22:33.79,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}If I become normal, can I stay close?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.25,0:22:39.30,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}With the children, we link our arms
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.55,0:22:44.43,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}Make a circle and sing a song
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.72,0:22:51.18,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5}Knowing there was no chair for me all along
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.18,0:22:54.19,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}You locked me into the dark
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.19,0:22:56.36,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}I’m your preserved flower
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.36,0:23:00.03,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}The world is too slow to understand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.03,0:23:02.11,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}Not all blossoms spark
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.11,0:23:03.78,ED-EN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(240,240)\blur5\c&HFFFFFF&\3c&HBE474B&}And spikes may be sharp
